 in seconds.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon?2046d82c3af66eee\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-78c92fac7aa8fdd8.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 antialiased\"><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-100\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-pulse-600 font-bold text-lg hover:text-pulse-700\" href=\"/\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 17h8m0 0V9m0 8l-8-8-4 4-6-6\"></path></svg>AnswerPulse</a><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-20 h-8 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg animate-pulse\"></div></nav></div></header><section class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-20 pt-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-pulse-50/50 to-gray-50\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-pulse-100 text-pulse-700 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium mb-6\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-pulse-600 rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>AEO Scanner</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5 leading-tight\">Is Your Page Ready for<!-- --> <span class=\"text-pulse-600\">Answer Engines</span>?</h1><p class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Scan any URL and get an instant AEO (Answer Engine Optimization) score across 8 key dimensions. Fast, no signup required.</p></div><form class=\"w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex gap-0 mb-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors border-b-2 bg-white border-pulse-600 text-pulse-700\">🔗 URL Scan</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors border-b-2 bg-gray-100 border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700\">📋 Paste HTML</button></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl rounded-tl-none border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative\"><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Enter URL to scan (e.g., https://example.com/blog/faq)\" class=\"w-full px-5 py-4 focus:outline-none text-lg pr-12\" value=\"\"/><svg class=\"absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-100 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50/50 flex justify-end\"><button type=\"submit\" disabled=\"\" class=\"px-8 py-3 bg-pulse-600 hover:bg-pulse-700 disabled:bg-gray-300 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-pulse-600/25 min-w-[140px] flex items-center justify-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg>Analyze</button></div></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center\">By analyzing, you agree to our<!-- --> <a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"underline hover:text-gray-600\">Privacy Policy</a></p></form><div class=\"mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Secure &amp; private</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Results in seconds</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path d=\"M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z\"></path></svg>8-dimension analysis</div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-4\">Why AEO Matters</h2><p class=\"text-center text-gray-500 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Answer engines (AI Overviews, ChatGPT, Perplexity) are changing how users find information. Optimize for answers, not just clicks.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">📊</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Structured Data Check</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Detect FAQ, Article, and HowTo schemas that answer engines rely on for direct answers.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">❓</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Q&amp;A Format Analysis</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Identify question-answer patterns that match how AI models extract and present information.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">✍️</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Readability Score</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Calculate Flesch Reading Ease to ensure content is accessible for both users and AI.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">🏗️</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Heading Structure</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Verify proper H1-H3 hierarchy and question-word usage for better content parsing.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">🏆</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Authority Signals</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Check for author attribution, publication dates, and citation links that boost trust.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-pulse-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all bg-gray-50/50\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-3\">📱</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Mobile Readiness</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Ensure viewport, language tags, and responsive patterns for mobile-first indexing.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Ready to Check Your AEO Score?</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 mb-8\">Enter any URL and get your detailed AEO report in seconds.</p><form class=\"w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex gap-0 mb-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors border-b-2 bg-white border-pulse-600 text-pulse-700\">🔗 URL Scan</button><button t